		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.urgency-badge {
		display: inline-block;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		color: white;
		padding: 10px 25px;
		border-radius: 30px;
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		margin-bottom: 30px;
